<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cidade dos Anjos • Ultimate Fan Hub</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --purple-deep: #0d0420;
            --purple-dark: #1a0933;
            --purple-main: #4c1d95;
            --purple-bright: #7c3aed;
            --purple-light: #a78bfa;
            --purple-glow: #8b5cf6;
            --accent-pink: #db2777;
            --accent-cyan: #06b6d4;
            --bg-dark: #030014;
            --text-primary: #e0e7ff;
            --text-secondary: #a5b4fc;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, var(--purple-deep) 100%);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.12) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(76, 29, 149, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-bright) 0%, var(--accent-pink) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.3s both;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        .tab-btn {
            background: rgba(107, 47, 181, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid var(--purple-main);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .tab-btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .tab-btn:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .tab-btn:hover {
            border-color: var(--purple-bright);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .tab-btn.active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-main), var(--accent-pink));
            border-color: var(--accent-pink);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.5);
        }

        .tab-content {
            display: none;
            animation: slideIn 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .tab-content.active {
            display: block;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(26, 9, 51, 0.7);
            border: 1px solid var(--purple-main);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: var(--purple-bright);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--purple-light);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        h3 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--purple-bright);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .bingo-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .bingo-cell {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107, 47, 181, 0.3), rgba(45, 22, 84, 0.5));
            border: 2px solid var(--purple-main);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            min-height: 120px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .bingo-cell:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-main), var(--purple-dark));
            transform: scale(1.05);
            border-color: var(--purple-bright);
        }

        .bingo-cell.marked {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-pink), var(--purple-bright));
            border-color: var(--accent-pink);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.5);
        }

        .playlist-item {
            background: rgba(107, 47, 181, 0.2);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--purple-bright);
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .playlist-item:hover {
            background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
            border-left-color: var(--accent-pink);
            transform: translateX(8px);
        }

        .character-selector {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .character-btn {
            background: rgba(107, 47, 181, 0.3);
            border: 2px solid var(--purple-main);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .character-btn:hover,
        .character-btn.active {
            background: var(--purple-bright);
            border-color: var(--accent-pink);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.4);
        }

        .episode-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(45, 22, 84, 0.7), rgba(26, 9, 51, 0.7));
            border: 1px solid var(--purple-main);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .episode-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--purple-bright);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
        }

        .episode-title {
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--purple-light);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .episode-meta {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .note-input {
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(26, 9, 51, 0.6);
            border: 2px solid var(--purple-main);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
        }

        .note-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--purple-bright);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
        }

        .btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-main), var(--purple-bright));
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(107, 47, 181, 0.4);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5);
        }

        .moodboard-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .mood-card {
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-dark), var(--purple-main));
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .mood-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent);
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            transition: all 0.6s;
        }

        .mood-card:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .mood-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05) rotate(2deg);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.4);
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107, 47, 181, 0.3), rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2));
            border: 1px solid var(--purple-bright);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple-bright), var(--accent-pink));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .stat-label {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .language-card {
            background: rgba(45, 22, 84, 0.6);
            border: 2px solid var(--purple-main);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            background: rgba(26, 9, 51, 0.8);
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple-bright), var(--accent-pink));
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: width 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5);
        }

        .floating-particles {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .particle {
            position: absolute;
            background: var(--purple-bright);
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.1;
            animation: float 15s infinite ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
            25% { transform: translateY(-20px) translateX(10px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-40px) translateX(-10px); }
            75% { transform: translateY(-20px) translateX(5px); }
        }

        .search-box {
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(26, 9, 51, 0.6);
            border: 2px solid var(--purple-main);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .search-box:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--purple-bright);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .tabs {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .tab-btn {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .bingo-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }

            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="floating-particles" id="particles"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>CIDADE DOS ANJOS</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Ultimate Fan Hub • Soukateh Edition</p>
        </header>

        <div class="tabs">
            <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="openTab('dashboard')">Dashboard</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('bingo')">RP Bingo</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('playlists')">Playlists</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('episodes')">Episode Guide</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('notebook')">Meu Caderno</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('learning')">Learning Hub</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('moodboard')">Aesthetic Board</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('storytelling')">Storytelling</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('aitraining')">🤖 AI Training</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('familytree')">🌳 Árvore</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('wardrobe')">Wardrobe</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('radio')">RP Radio</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('predictor')">Story Predictor</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('filters')">Filters</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('pomodoro')">Pomodoro</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('study')">Study Playlists</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('flashcards')">Flashcards</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('goals')">Goals RPG</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('reading')">Reading List</button>
        </div>

        <!-- DASHBOARD -->
        <div id="dashboard" class="tab-content active">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>🎯 Seu Hub Definitivo</h2>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">6</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Anos Acompanhando</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">1</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Ano com Soukateh</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">3</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Personagens Favoritos</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">∞</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Momentos Épicos</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>🎭 Personagens da Soukateh</h3>
                <div class="character-selector">
                    <button class="character-btn active">Kate Higanbana</button>
                    <button class="character-btn">Duna Beaumont</button>
                    <button class="character-btn">Marcela Garcia</button>
                </div>
                <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
                    Kate Higanbana é a personagem principal da Soukateh, com uma história rica e complexa que se desenvolve há anos. 
                    Sua jornada na Cidade dos Anjos é repleta de altos e baixos, relacionamentos marcantes e momentos inesquecíveis.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>🎵 Músicas do Momento</h3>
                <div class="playlist-item">
                    <strong>Jão</strong> - Idiota
                </div>
                <div class="playlist-item">
                    <strong>Carol Biazin</strong> - Amor Traumatizado
                </div>
                <div class="playlist-item">
                    <strong>Madison Beer</strong> - Reckless
                </div>
                <div class="playlist-item">
                    <strong>Maggie Lindemann</strong> - Pretty Girl
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BINGO -->
        <div id="bingo" class="tab-content">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>🎲 RP Bingo Generator</h2>
                <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Clique nas células para marcar quando acontecer durante a live!
                </p>
                <button class="btn" onclick="generateBingo()">Gerar Novo Bingo</button>
                <div class="bingo-grid" id="bingoGrid">
                    <!-- Será preenchido pelo JavaScript -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- PLAYLISTS -->
        <div id="playlists" class="tab-content">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>🎵 Character Playlist Generator</h2>
                <div class="character-selector">
                    <button class="character-btn" onclick="showPlaylist('kate')">Kate Higanbana</button>
                    <button class="character-btn" onclick="showPlaylist('duna')">Duna Beaumont</button>
                    <button class="character-btn" onclick="showPlaylist('marcela')">Marcela Garcia</button>
                    <button class="character-btn" onclick="showPlaylist('meraki')">Gangue Meraki</button>
                </div>
                <div id="playlistContent" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Selecione um personagem para ver a playlist recomendada!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- EPISODES -->
        <div id="episodes" class="tab-content">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>📺 RP Episode Guide</h2>
                <input type="text" class="search-box" placeholder="Buscar por arco, personagem ou data..." 
                       onkeyup="filterEpisodes(this.value)">
                <div id="episodeList">
                    <div class="episode-card" data-search="kate romance início">
                        <div class="episode-title">O Início de Kate na Cidade</div>
                        <div class="episode-meta">Personagem: Kate Higanbana • Época: 2024</div>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
                            Kate chega à Cidade dos Anjos e começa sua jornada. Primeiros encontros, primeiras amizades
                            e o início de uma história épica.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="episode-card" data-search="meraki gangue ação">
                        <div class="episode-title">Kate e a Meraki</div>
                        <div class="episode-meta">Personagem: Kate Higanbana • Época: 2024</div>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
                            A conexão de Kate com a gangue Meraki se fortalece. Momentos de tensão, lealdade e ação.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="episode-card" data-search="duna mistério drama">
                        <div class="episode-title">Os Mistérios de Duna Beaumont</div>
                        <div class="episode-meta">Personagem: Duna Beaumont • Época: 2025</div>
                        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
                            Duna entra em cena com sua personalidade única e história intrigante.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- NOTEBOOK -->
        <div id="notebook" class="tab-content">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>📔 Meu Caderno de RP</h2>
                <h3>Minhas Anotações</h3>
                <textarea class="note-input" id="personalNotes" placeholder="Escreva suas teorias, observações e momentos favoritos aqui...">Kate está desenvolvendo um relacionamento interessante com...

Teoria: Acho que a Duna vai se envolver em...

Momento favorito: Quando Kate disse aquela frase icônica na live de...</textarea>
                <button class="btn" onclick="saveNotes()">Salvar Notas</button>
                
                <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Teorias e Previsões</h3>
                <textarea class="note-input" id="theories" placeholder="Suas teorias sobre o que vai acontecer...">Previsão: A Kate vai finalmente confrontar...

Teoria da Meraki: Acredito que a gangue vai...</textarea>
                <button class="btn" onclick="saveTheories()">Salvar Teorias</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- LEARNING HUB -->
        <div id="learning" class="tab-content">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>🌍 Learning Hub</h2>
                <div class="language-card">
                    <h3>Inglês (B2) 🇬🇧</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Vocabulário do RP em inglês</p>
                    <div class="progress-bar">
                        <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 75%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="language-card">
                    <h3>Espanhol (Básico) 🇪🇸</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Frases comuns no GTA RP</p>
                    <div class="progress-bar">
                        <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 30%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="language-card">
                    <h3>Francês (Iniciante) 🇫🇷</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Começando a aprender</p>
                    <div class="progress-bar">
                        <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 15%"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Frases do RP para Praticar</h3>
                <div class="playlist-item">
                    <strong>EN:</strong> "What's going on here?" - O que está acontecendo aqui?
                </div>
                <div class="playlist-item">
                    <strong>ES:</strong> "¿Dónde está la fiesta?" - Onde está a festa?
                </div>
                <div class="playlist-item">
                    <strong>FR:</strong> "Qu'est-ce qui se passe?" - O que está acontecendo?
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MOODBOARD -->
